      <title>调查显示，英国保守党在工党压倒性胜利中面临历史性损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-tories-face-historic-loss-amid-labour-landslide-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据代表“Best for Britain”的 Survation 进行的一项民意调查，英国执政的保守党面临着最糟糕的选举结果，工党预计将在下次大选中赢得超过 70% 的席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-tories-face-historic-loss-amid-labour-landslide-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:27:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
